00:17:59.296 --> 00:18:00.466 A:middle
You saw on the trailer,
there are a lot

00:18:00.466 --> 00:18:02.946 A:middle
of different characters
in this upcoming film

00:18:03.006 --> 00:18:06.066 A:middle
and each character presents its
