the new Mac Pro,
it's unreleased.

00:25:56.906 --> 00:25:59.756 A:middle
We're running on an unreleased
OS and the software, MARI,

00:25:59.756 --> 00:26:01.446 A:middle
has only been on the
Mac for about six weeks.

