00:28:42.766 --> 00:28:43.866 A:middle
I'm trying to keep this--

00:28:44.086 --> 00:28:47.696 A:middle
these shapes graphic
and really strong here,

00:28:48.096 --> 00:28:51.696 A:middle
get that simple idea
