WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:30:58.326 --> 00:31:00.356 A:middle
Add some freckles, a
little bit of darkening.

00:31:00.666 --> 00:31:01.966 A:middle
And I can put some stuff on

