And it's just because there's
this really cool vein doing this

00:31:45.136 --> 00:31:45.906 A:middle
really cool thing.

00:31:46.556 --> 00:31:49.526 A:middle
And it's not, you know, I'm
not trying to be insulting,

00:31:49.526 --> 00:31:51.476 A:middle
it's just that I'm
fascinated by it, right?

00:31:52.166 --> 00:31:53.936 A:middle
Because I'm going to use it to--

00:31:53.936 --> 00:31:55.756 A:middle
on the next day when I'm
painting this character.

00:31:55.876 --> 00:31:57.226 A:middle
So, anyway.

00:31:57.676 --> 00:32:00.276 A:middle
I hope I haven't
offended too many people.

WEBVTT
